org.ptolemy.ptango.lib

Class HttpResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ptolemy.ptango.lib.HttpResponse

  • public class HttpResponse
extends java.lang.Object
    An HTTP response, comprised of selected fields from an HttpURLConnection. Useful for classes that want response data but should not have authority to open and close connections.
    Since:
    Ptolemy II 10.0
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    Marten Lohstroh, Elizabeth Latronico
    See Also:
    HttpGet, HttpPost, HttpPut
    Accepted Rating:
    Red (eal)
    Proposed Rating:
    Red (eal)
